snippet: Caleb Lawrence McGillvary, who earlier this year used a hatchet to hit a man who had struck a utility worker with his car, was arrested on Thursday night.
lead_paragraph: Caleb Lawrence McGillvary, who earlier this year used a hatchet to hit a man who had struck a utility worker with his car, was arrested on Thursday night.
